body remember that ?) - DaggerFall - Heros - hell the list go on and on - you could even say that games like Warcraft - and Starcraft (in single player mode) are like this.... (you get access to new buildings and units as you procced the game - and you HAVE to complete level 1 to get to level 2....<P>One think I DO see - is the Guild improvement thing - instead of YOU improve your char - YOU will help improve the guild as hole - and THAT sounds interesting - as long as there realy is a difference.<BR>I also see the hidden race thinks as something to look forward to - but fear that its gona be to easy to get em - I mean if it only takes 1 month to get level 70 - how hard can it be to get access to thoses races - well I realy dono  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P><BR>Umm dono if I lost track of my post  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"> - but I think you get the idea - I want something to lookforward to in a game - I see the guild improvent as an interestion idea - but what about me... hehe<P>Take care all<P>Trivan Valliant<BR>55th Mage - Crazy Dane
