The soft caps are one of the reasons why I think SB is going to surprise all the nay-sayers...  I believe SB is going to have one of the best roleplay communities in the business.  <P>People playing after the first several months are going to be doing so for the -interaction- between players.  That could be wars, trades, empire-building, etc.<P>The other reason is that WP's fiction appears to match the game mechanics.  In my years of learning to be a GM I found that a consistent GM that makes sense is a good GM.<P>Keep in mind, there's no limit on empire building.  A character may get maxed, but an empire can always get bigger/stronger.<P>--------------------<P>Feher Hinan<BR>Fury, Phaedra's Children<BR>The Crimson Empire
