I think it'll be great. I'd prolly get up to lvl 80 or so and then go exploring, raiding, jumping people  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0">.  You people make it seem like leveling is fun!?!  I know for sure lvling in eq just plain SUCKS.  I'd rather go raise money, or just have some fun.  And its not like you CANT level anymore, its just the gains start to become less, im guessing stop altogether around the 100s.  And it will show your power to get up there in those lvls, a lvl 60 might not back down to a 70, but he prolly will to a 100.
